      • getStorageForKey

        public CNIStorage getStorageForKey(java.lang.String key)
        Returns the storage that contains object with specified key. First it checks memory storage (cache). If object with specified key wasn't found then the persistent storage will be checked.
        Parameters:
        key - key of an object to find
        Returns:
        storage that contains object for this key, null - if object with such key wasn't found in any storage
